On Tue, 9 Sep 2003, paul wrote:

> I just bought a 72 today.  On the front of the van, just above the left
> headlight there was a rubber plug/gasket covering a hole with what looked to
> be three screw holes surrounding it.  Anyone know any reason why that would be
> there or was someone just trying to install something after they bought it.

It sounds like the hole left when a "ball mount" antenna mount is removed
from the body.  These mounts are used for CB and other communications
antennas.


